            "parent": 8,
            "text": "were 15.82 lg / ml for chrysophanol and 17.39 lg / ml for aloe - emodin , respectively . <S>",
            "relation": "SAME-UNIT"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "Virucidal activity of agents correlated with anti - JEV activity ,",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "while virucidal IC 50 values were 7.58 lg / ml for methanol extract , 17.36 lg / ml for water extract , 0.75 lg / ml for chrysophanol and 0.46 lg / ml for aloe - emodin , respectively . <S> <P>",
            "relation": "COMPARISON"
        },
        {
